title: Woman shares before and after pic of herself at 25 and 42
text: 'Age is just a number!' Woman posts pictures of herself wearing a bikini aged 25 and almost two decades later after having three kids... and says she feels 'fitter at 42 than ever before' Sheree Paltridge, 42, from Queensland, became a bodybuilder in 2015 After entering a bodybuilding comp she lost seven per cent of her body fat Ms Paltridge said she ate the same way as her daughters, aged 13, 11 and six She is now a bodybuilding champion and flaunted her figure in a throwback pic The image showed her at 25 and at 42 and the change is undeniable Published: 02:01 GMT, 21 February 2017 | Updated: 02:34 GMT, 21 February 2017 108 shares
